<h1>Chat Room Guidelines</h1>
<p>The toki pona community has been using about 10 different online forums over the past 10 years, mailing lists etc, and all of them have seen their share of spam and other bad behavior, a very few fights, many arguments (and some of those productive ones!), and lots of abrasiveness. This document is to encourage the community to get along-- it's mostly taken from other document I found on the web.</p>
